                     </persName>
                   of the Stock Exchange gentleman, with intent to defraud the 
                     <persName id="t18160529-49-victim470" type="victimName">
                        <rs id="t18160529-49-viclabel270" type="occupation">Governor and Company of the Bank of England</rs>
