                     <interp inst="t18160529-49-person484" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , esq. chief accountant to the Bank of England; whether you signed a power of attorney on the 15th instant, in the presence of 
               <persName id="t18160529-49-person485">
                  Thomas 
                  Walker
               <interp inst="t18160529-49-person485" type="surname" value="Walker"></interp>
