                     <interp inst="t18160529-49-person485" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , an attorney, at Dartford, to transfer seven hundred and eighty-one pounds, being a third part of two thousand three hundred and forty-three pounds eleven shillings and ten-pence, navy five per cents annuities, which 
               <persName id="t18160529-49-person486">
                  John 
                  Austen
               <interp inst="t18160529-49-person486" type="surname" value="Austen"></interp>
